ECM Real Estate Investments Tumbles 10%, Extending Week’s Slide

-- B y   K r y s t o f   C h a m o n i k o l a s
-- 
2011-04-13T12:14:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-13/ecm-real-estate-investments-tumbles-10-extending-week-s-slide.html
ECM Real Estate Investments AG (ECM)  fell
10 percent to 59.5 koruna by 1:56 p.m. in  Prague , extending the
Czech property developer’s drop so far this week to 27 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Krystof Chamonikolas in Prague at 
